<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c76803d2425f1b98d6e5255db0fcebb5>.
<#c76803d2425f1b98d6e5255db0fcebb5> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2cb9200d-57a3-4068-8157-5706fd0c587b>;
