_:b0__9857 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.4832 68.38665,24.14562 68.38665,24.14562 55.53168,11.4832 55.53168,11.4832 68.38665))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
