    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Photogrammetric 3D model of a helmet fragment from the Vendel period with pressed-plate ornamentation. A shield is clearly visible in the ornamentation. Excavated from Vendel Boat Grave XI/Boat Grave 11 in Vendel, Uppsala, it is currently held in the collections of the National Historical Museums in Stockholm. \n\nLink to the Dynamic Collections platform  \n\nhttps://dyncoll.ht.lu.se/artifact_view.php?item=985\n\nLink to Sök I Samlingarna  \n\nhttps://samlingar.shm.se/object/49e84c3c-20e6-4fba-87f9-38e62cd313d3"@en;
