    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Photogrammetric 3D model of a helmet fragment from the Vendel period with pressed-plate ornamentation. Excavated from Vendel Boat Grave XI/Boat Grave 11 in Vendel, Uppsala, it is currently held in the collections of the National Historical Museums in Stockholm. \n\nLink to the Dynamic Collections platform  \n\nhttps://dyncoll.ht.lu.se/artifact_view.php?item=979\n\nLink to Sök I Samlingarna  \n\nhttps://samlingar.shm.se/object/990c9715-0a19-42cf-a3f6-2ad8b2d7373e"@en;
