    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021004953>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "3D photogrammetric model of an iron helmet fragment with pressed plate decoration of a bird figure and textile remnants preserved by corrosion. Excavated from Vendel Boat Grave XI in Vendel, Uppsala, it dates from the eponymous Vendel period and is currently held in the collections of the National Historical Museums in Stockholm. \n\nLink to the Dynamic Collections platform \n\nhttps://dyncoll.ht.lu.se/artifact_view.php?item=978 \n\nLink to Sök I Samlingarna  \n\nhttps://samlingar.shm.se/object/9c20477a-4d41-4080-b1fa-cf9eaa171ef1"@en;
