<https://doi.org/10.5878/002982> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__55904.
_:b0__55904 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
