_:b0__62453 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Skolinspektionens enkät Pedagogisk personal gymnasieskola"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N17331> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-05-29"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
